<gloss rendition="OuterMarginalLine:gloss"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_fab2cabc">xxui</ab></gloss>
<ab facs="#eSc_line_d5441d69" type="textline">ulba dubietate. cum primo post accasum solis apparet non iam supra illum sed</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_42c77cb6" type="textline">iuxta illum ad meridiem posita uidetur.,  atq, ideo aquilonalia eius latera solea</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_05e807a5" type="textline">spectante. cernitur erecta progredi., semꝑ enim luna auersis a sole cornibus rotun</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_c0697c0e" type="textline">dam sui partem pandit ad illum cuius ordine rationis agitur.- ut quo dies longior eo sit</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_755939f4" type="textline">luna nouia excelsior., &amp; quo breuior atq, ad merediem decliuior est dies eo deiectior noua</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:gloss"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_dd1b83ff">i. humilior.</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_25388596" type="textline">luna cernatur., &amp; in deuulgi creuit opinio lunam cum supina &amp; celsior incedit turbines</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_fef12a0d" type="textline">tempestatum.- cum uero erecta &amp; in austros deiectior tranquillitatem designare. qui ais</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_a705b110" type="textline">nimirum status est anni uertentis ut sex mensibus quib, decrescit dies multo cle</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_770d6d88" type="textline">mentior sit aeris motus quam reliquis sex., eadem ratio est &amp;iam lunae decrescentis</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_5e9729c1" type="textline">quare matutino in exortu nunc erecta nunc supina pareat eadem; cur interdiu sae</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_e0d5b361" type="textline">pe prona procedat nimirum solis eam radiis superiore ex loco tangentib,; non ergo</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_197cd3ca" type="textline">lunae conuersio quae naturalis est &amp; fixa potest futuri mensis portendere statũ</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_4f6571ec" type="textline">sed qui curiosi sunt huius modi rerum. coloris uel eius uel solis uel cȩli ipsius.</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_48512f39" type="textline">aut stellarum siue nubium motatione. uel aliis quibus libet indiciis saepesta</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_a4f3392d" type="textline">tum aeris qui sit futurus explorant., deniq, lunam quartam si pura fuerit neq,</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_57beada7" type="textline">obtusis cornib,. dare reliquis diebus usq, ad exactum mensem indicium serenitatis</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:gloss"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_fed12f4f">n</ab></gloss><ab facs="#eSc_line_ebeee311" subtype="heading" type="textline">existimant &amp;cet talia., QUA RATIONE LUNA CUM SIT SITU INFERIOR SUPERIOR</ab><ab facs="#eSc_line_88fe0c6c" subtype="heading" type="textline">SOLE ALIQUOTIES UIDEATUR.</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_8d51883b" type="textline">Nec mirari opus est cum lunam per australia signa currentem multo infe</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_8b7d3934" type="textline">rius á cui cinius terrae quam solẽ. cum hisdem moratur in partibus circuire</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_76e3f349" type="textline">uiderimus., quae uidelicet multo inferior non solum sole sed &amp; ueneri ac mercurio</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:correction"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_648e338f">quia</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_29dcb6b8" type="textline">quae infime stellarum sunt. luna in confinio aeris huius turbolenti. &amp; puri decurrit</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_02181b20" type="textline">aetheris., deniq, multi philosophorum solem ab esse a luna. unde uiginti partes</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_d7736db2" type="textline">quantas lunam ipsam a terra prodiderunt; pithagoras uero uir sagacis ammi a t̃ra</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:addition"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_5e9f28a9">.usq;</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_d1f1fc86" type="textline">ad lunam. cxxui milia stadiarum e͠e colligit; ad solem ab ea duplum. inde ad xii signa</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_102129d9" type="textline">triplicatum., sed merito querere ac mirari sollicitus quisq, potest quare luna</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_1b86ee88" type="textline">in solstitiali circulo decurrens. quanto altior aestiuo sole currere. tanto breuiores</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_4d41c7a5" type="textline">uideatur facere umbras., unde paucis intimandum est quod hunc lunȩ progresũ</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_5eb01855" type="textline">ultra solem inutraq, caeliplaga. &amp; australi uidelicet &amp; septentrionali. signiferi</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_c669929f" type="textline">gignat latitudo., porro in australi ipsa quoq, lunȩ eiusdem deiectio iuuet. si</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_eab074cf" type="textline">quidem signifer idem. ccctis. quidem lxu partibus &amp; quadrante. ꝑ cȩli ambitum</ab> <ab facs="#eSc_line_ae55369d" type="textline">longus sed duodecim est partib, latus. harum duas tantũ medias sol luna omnes per</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:addition"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_ad1e0a2d">uͦ</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_6854c217" type="textline">uagare consueuit., quȩ cum australes illius deuenit in locos. aliquanto humilior</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:gloss"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_854b7a93">fere</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_86faecad" type="textline">hiƀno sole appar&amp;. non solẹm quia uicinior est terrae. sed etiam quia .u. partib,</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:correction"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_79d249cf">u</ab></gloss> <ab facs="#eSc_line_429c2614" type="textline">aliquoties siue etam ui solaris cursus terminos in meridiem transit. &amp; quanto am</ab><gloss rendition="InterlinearLine:correction"><ab ana="#glossline" facs="#eSc_line_0c13a4d6"/></gloss>
